    <constraint source="project">**NFR-07 BINDING: pre-fill hook signatures + 45s timeout + `useAiPrefill` UNCHANGED.** Only the data field `outputSchema` is populated. Before/after pre-fill regression test REQUIRED. If ANY signature, timing, or behavior differs after the migration — STOP and ROLL BACK.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">**Schema change escalation gate per CLAUDE.md Confirmation Triggers; user confirmation required at start of task.** Binding-sensitive production action — agent MUST pause and confirm.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-07">`MatterPreFillService`, `ProjectPreFillService`, `useAiPrefill` hook, `findBestLookupMatch`, `AiFieldTag`, 45s timeout, `$choices`-constrained output contract, `Workspace:PreFillPlaybookId` config — ALL UNCHANGED. R6 may extend `IWorkspacePrefillAi` with new methods but existing signatures stay.</constraint>
