  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + RIGOR LEVEL + Confirmation Gate">
      Check context. Declare:

      ```
      🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL
      📋 REASON: NFR-07 BINDING — pre-fill flow is binding-sensitive; before/after
                 regression test required; CLAUDE.md Confirmation Trigger
      📖 PROTOCOL STEPS: all 12 steps below INCLUDING Step 9.5 quality gates + explicit
                         pre-fill regression test (Step 7)
      Proceeding with Step 0...
      ```

      **PAUSE and confirm with user**: (a) approved to migrate matter-prefill action's
      `outputSchema` data field only; (b) confirm NO changes to `IWorkspacePrefillAi`,
      `MatterPreFillService`, `useAiPrefill`, or the 45s timeout are being made.
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress + Capture Pre-State">
      Read TASK-INDEX.md; confirm 034 status 🔲; deps (030, 031) complete. Capture the
      current state of the matter-prefill action row + node via GET — save full JSON to
      `notes/task-034-pre-migration-state.json`.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">
      Read inputs + knowledge. Read `WORKSPACE-AI-PREFILL-GUIDE.md` IN FULL. Read
      `IWorkspacePrefillAi.cs` IN FULL — capture exact method signatures + parameter
      types. Read the existing `$choices`-constrained output contract (JPS source for
      matter-prefill action).
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="BEFORE Pre-Fill Regression Test">
      Run a full end-to-end pre-fill on a designated test matter document. Capture:
      (a) all wizard fields populated;
      (b) per-field values produced;
      (c) end-to-end latency;
      (d) any console / server logs.
      Record in `notes/task-034-prefill-regression-test.md`. This is the BEFORE
      baseline.
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Author the JSON Schema Document">
      Create `infra/dataverse/outputschemas/matter-prefill.schema.json`. Mirror the
      existing `$choices`-constrained output EXACTLY — every field name + type + nullable
      flag matches today's wizard consumer contract. Validate against draft-07
      meta-schema.
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Author Migration Script">
      Create `scripts/Migrate-MatterPrefillActionOutputSchema.ps1`:
      (a) GET action by alternate key;
      (b) Guard + PATCH `sprk_outputschema`;
      (c) GET playbook node; PATCH `destination = form-prefill` per task 031 storage
          surface;
      (d) Log all actions.
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Apply to Spaarke Dev">
      Run script. Capture output + post-migration row state in
      `notes/task-034-migration-evidence.md`.
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="AFTER Pre-Fill Regression Test (BINDING)">
      Run the SAME end-to-end pre-fill against the SAME test matter document. Capture
      the SAME data points: wizard fields populated; per-field values; end-to-end
      latency; logs. Diff against the BEFORE baseline in
      `notes/task-034-prefill-regression-test.md`.

      **Acceptance criterion**: ZERO diff in per-field wizard output values. Latency
      within ±10% of BEFORE baseline. NO error or warning that wasn't present BEFORE.

      If ANY divergence detected: STOP, run the rollback script (capture in evidence
      notes), escalate to user before proceeding.
    </step>
    <step order="8" name="Verify Idempotency">
      Re-run migration script. Confirm no-op. Re-run AFTER pre-fill test to confirm no
      drift across migration runs.
    </step>
    <step order="9" name="Verify Acceptance Criteria">
      Walk through every &lt;acceptance-criterion&gt; below. Record evidence.
    </step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL rigor)">
      Run `code-review` skill against script + schema. Run `adr-check`; verify ADR-013
      (facade boundary preserved — no signatures changed), ADR-027 (solution management),
      ADR-029 (publish-size delta = 0), NFR-07 (binding — explicit confirmation that no
      pre-fill flow signatures, timeout, or hook is touched). Both gates MUST pass.
    </step>
    <step order="10" name="Document + Complete">
      Update TASK-INDEX.md: 034 🔲 → ✅. Reset `current-task.md`. Report completion with
      explicit confirmation that NFR-07 binding is honored + regression test passed.
    </step>
  </steps>

